# Fitted Formats - Four Sub-formats Strategy

## Core Concept

Create 4 subformats that activate based on container size:
- **Badge** (≤150px width, <170px height)
- **Strip** (>150px width, <170px height)
- **Tile** (<400px width, ≥170px height)
- **Card** (≥400px width, ≥170px height)

## Container Size Decision Tree

```
Container Size
    │
    ├─ Height < 170px (Horizontal)
    │   ├─ Width ≤ 150px → BADGE
    │   └─ Width > 150px → STRIP
    │
    └─ Height ≥ 170px (Vertical)
        ├─ Width < 400px → TILE
        └─ Width ≥ 400px → CARD
```

## Container Query Skeleton

```css
.fitted-container {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

.badge-format, .strip-format, .tile-format, .card-format {
  display: none;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  padding: clamp(0.375rem, 3%, 0.75rem);
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

@container (max-width: 150px) and (max-height: 169px) {
  .badge-format { display: flex; }
}

@container (min-width: 151px) and (max-height: 169px) {
  .strip-format { display: flex; }
}

@container (max-width: 399px) and (min-height: 170px) {
  .tile-format { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
}

@container (min-width: 400px) and (min-height: 170px) {
  .card-format { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
}
```

## Subformat Rules

**Badge:**
- Exportable graphics feel
- Left-aligned
- Images: 16-34px
- Heights: 40px (horizontal), 65px (stacked), 105px (magnetic edges)

**Strip:**
- Dropdown/chooser panels
- Title MUST ALWAYS be visible
- Left-aligned
- Images: 20-34px at 40px, 40px at 65px+

**Tile:**
- Standard vertical card
- Grid viewing
- Primary identity fully visible
- Last element magnetically sticks to bottom

**Card:**
- 400×170: Horizontal split at golden ratio
- Larger: Vertically subdivided
- Expanded MUST use all vertical space

## Content Priority

1. Title/Name
2. Image
3. Short ID
4. Key Info
5. Badge/Status
6. Metadata
7. Description
8. CTA (hover only)

## Typography Hierarchy

- **Size cascade:** 80-87% per level (1em → 0.875em → 0.75em)
- **Weight cascade:** Drop 100-200 units per level
- **Spacing cascade:** 50% → 37.5% → 25%
